Answers are:<br>
<br>
1 - Who is the blue mage?  A:  Tenser<br>
<br>
2 - Who betrayed the Circle of Eight? A: Rary<br>
<br>
3 - What were the sphere, the cone and the cube for? A: to access different part of Lolth's Demonweb from the Descent to the Depths, Vault of the Drow and Queen of the Demonweb Pits series.<br>
